<div class="calcpad-output">
 <!-- Section properties of a channel (U) profile: area, centroid, $I_x$, $I_y$, section moduli and radii of gyration. -->
 <h3>Geometrical Properties of Channel Section</h3>
 <div style="max-width:120mm">
  <img alt="channel.png" class="side" src="Images/mechanics/sections/channel.png" style="height:150pt;"/>
 </div>
 <p>Dimensions</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>h</var>
   =
   <u class="input-5">20</u>
  </span>
  m,
  <span class="eq">
   <var>t</var>
   <sub>w</sub>
   =
   <u class="input-5">1</u>
  </span>
  m
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
