   ·
   <var>t</var>
   <sub>w</sub>
   = 20 · 1 = 20
  </span>
  m
  <sup>2</sup>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>A</var>
   <sub>f</sub>
   =  (
   <var>b</var>
   <sub>f</sub>
   −
   <var>t</var>
   <sub>w</sub>
   )  ·
   <var>t</var>
   <sub>f</sub>
   =  ( 10 − 1 )  · 2 = 18
  </span>
  m
  <sup>2</sup>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>A</var>
   =
   <var>A</var>
   <sub>w</sub>
   + 2 ·
   <var>A</var>
   <sub>f</sub>
   = 20 + 2 · 18 = 56
  </span>
  m
  <sup>2</sup>
 </p>
 <p>Centroid</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>S</var>
   <sub>z</sub>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    <var>A</var>
    <sub>w</sub>
    ·
    <var>t</var>
    <sub>w</sub>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
